title: China's Chips troubled by U.S. Toughest export controls/A massive wave of chip companies closed

media:group.media:title: China's Chips troubled by U.S. Toughest export controls/A massive wave of chip companies closed
media:group.media:description:
Chips making chips or Robots making Fries! This is happening in America. The Chinese Communist Party or CCP no doubt dreams about such an achievement. But on October 7, the American government almost crushed this dream of the CCP.  On that day, the US government issued a new regulation restricting the export of high-end chips and chip manufacturing equipment to China.
